item.title: CVE-2022-4548|2024-08-03T01:41:45.614Z -- unknown -- optimize%20images%20alt%20text%20%28alt%20tag%29%20%26%20names%20for%20seo%20using%20ai
item.description: The Optimize images ALT Text & names for SEO using AI WordPress plugin before 2.0.8 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged-in admin change them via a CSRF attack.
